     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           US     10
      *
     C           TNKEY     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           TTT1
     C                     KFLD           TTT2
     C                     KFLD           TTT3
     C                     KFLD           TTT4
